the big "D" himself,
Dave Garver.

05:48.098 --> 05:51.642
Dave, people, is gonna
bring you five hours
of mellow groove.

05:51.727 --> 05:53.519
So, in the meantime,
this is Sweet Al Monte saying

05:53.603 --> 05:57.273
hang in there, babies,
because everything is
going to be everything.

05:57.357 --> 05:58.482
Bye.

05:58.567 --> 05:59.859
