A biography, pictures.

06:10.162 --> 06:13.122
Oh, really? Is that
that Madge Brenner chick?

06:14.332 --> 06:16.375
Yeah, she's the one
putting it together.

06:16.460 --> 06:18.627
Well, in that case,
David, you're in.

06:20.756 --> 06:22.173
